T02D3643:256a-1: shr'i mnam h'a k'a la s'a dha nam /
T02D3643:256a-3: dpal ldan nag po chen po'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3643:256a-4: dpal ldan mgon po nag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3643:256a-5: de bzhin du sngon du gsungs pa'i rim pas stong
T02D3643:256a-6: pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes la sna tshogs padma dang
T02D3643:256a-7: nyi ma la h'um yig nag po de yongs su
T02D3643:256a-8: gyur pa las dpal ldan rje btsun nag po chen
T02D3643:256a-9: pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02D3643:256a-11: spyan gsum pa 'bar ba chen po /
T02D3643:256a-12: phyag g-yas pa dang g-yon pa dag gis gri gug dang thod pa bsnams pa /
T02D3643:256a-13: mgo bo'i phreng ba'i do shal gyis sku la brgyan pa /
T02D3643:256a-14: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du brdzes pa /
T02D3643:256b-0: sku thams cad la @256b sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
T02D3643:256b-2: zhal nas khrag 'dzag pa'i bdag nyid du skad cig gis bskyed nas sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02D3643:256b-4: aom ma h'a k'a la h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02D3643:256b-7: yungs kar rnams kyis nag po chen po la spos phul nas sran ma ma sha dang /
T02D3643:256b-11: byug pa lnga'i lcags kyu'i bdud rtsis nag po chen po mchod par bya ste /
T02D3643:256b-13: aom ma h'a k'a l'a ya /
T02D3643:256b-14: sh'a sa no pa h'a ri ni /
T02D3643:256b-15: ae sha pashtsi ma k'a lo /
T02D3643:256b-16: aa yam ai dam ratna tra ya /
T02D3643:256b-18: ya di pra t'idzny'a sma ra si ta d'a /
T02D3643:256b-20: kh'a hi kh'a hi ma ra ma ra grihna grihna /
T02D3643:256b-26: m'a ra ya h'um h'um phat phat /
T02D3643:256b-27: tsha ba gsum gyis bsgrub bya'i gzugs byas te lus
T02D3643:256b-28: la tsher mas dgang zhing dug dang ske tshe rnams
T02D3643:256b-29: kyis cho ga bzhin du byugs nas me la bsro
T02D3643:256b-30: bar bya'o // gang gi ming dang bcas pa de //
T02D3643:256b-31: de bzhin skad cig mthong mi 'gyur //
T02D3643:256b-32: slob dpon zhe sdang rtag khro gang //
T02D3643:256b-33: gang zhig dkon mchog gsum po dang //
T02D3643:256b-34: dpag med sems can rnams 'tshe rnams //
T02D3643:256b-35: nag po chen pos za bar byed //
T02D3643:256b-36: de yi lus kyi sha gcod cing //
T02D3643:256b-37: de bzhin khrag ni 'thung bar byed //
T02D3643:256b-38: spyi bor thig le byas nas gus pa chen po byas te bzlas pa'o //
